    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Streets of Rageness 是90年代经典的重塑版“打斗”游戏，背景设定在一个被犯罪侵袭、受无情集团控制的城市。在肆意的抢劫、混乱和破坏中，与敌人激战，成为街上最强的战士！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/43b47f32c7e96e1248212fc9d1d198b3.avif?t=1772360306\" width=616 height=99 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/d8f2cd9ba2180794ac34fc8506fa560f.poster.avif?t=1772360306\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/d8f2cd9ba2180794ac34fc8506fa560f.webm?t=1772360306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/d8f2cd9ba2180794ac34fc8506fa560f.mp4?t=1772360306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 Streets of Rageness</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streets of Rageness 将经典的打斗游戏公式提升到一个新水平，带来了身临其境的3D环境和动态战斗，灵感来源于像《街头霸王》和《铁拳》这样的经典格斗游戏。扮演各种街头斗士，每个角色都有独特的能力和战斗风格，在一系列艰难的城市竞技场中展开战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/cf01a3a6df479b3ada109035cc0cdff1.avif?t=1772360306\" width=616 height=99 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/a970c8e2aa7ec3c980d443567714418e.poster.avif?t=1772360306\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/a970c8e2aa7ec3c980d443567714418e.webm?t=1772360306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/a970c8e2aa7ec3c980d443567714418e.mp4?t=1772360306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握强大的拳脚组合，释放毁灭性的特殊技能，在快速节奏的打斗中与无情敌人作斗争。游戏提供了一个充满激情的物理体验，捕捉了老派动作游戏的精髓，带来了新的惊喜。探索详细的城市景观，击败强大的Boss，成为这部向经典《愤怒街道》系列致敬的终极街头战士。</p>",
